入款(<%= deposits.length %>笔) :
<% deposits.slice(0, 10).sort((a, b) => new Date(a.createdAt).getTime() - new Date(b.createdAt).getTime()).forEach((item, index) => { %><code><%= new Date(item.createdAt).toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour12: false }) %></code>  <strong><%= item.usdt_amount ? `${item.usdt_amount}u (${item.amount.toFixed(2)})` : item.amount %></strong>
<% }) %>
下发（<%= withdraws.length %>笔）:
<% withdraws.slice(0, 10).sort((a, b) => new Date(a.createdAt).getTime() - new Date(b.createdAt).getTime()).forEach((item, index) => { %><code><%= new Date(item.createdAt).toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour12: false }) %></code>  <strong><%= item.usdt_amount ? `${item.usdt_amount}u (${item.amount.toFixed(2)})` : item.amount %></strong>
<% }) %>
总入款: <%= deposits.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0).toFixed(2) %>
费率：<%= (feeRate).toFixed(2) %>%
汇总手续费: <%= summary %>
USD汇率: <%= exchangeRate %><% const totalDeposits = deposits.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) %><% const shouldPay = (totalDeposits * (1 - feeRate/100)).toFixed(2) %><% const totalWithdraws = withdraws.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) %><% const balance = (shouldPay - totalWithdraws).toFixed(2) %>
应下发: <%= shouldPay %>｜<%= (shouldPay/exchangeRate).toFixed(2) %> <%= unit %>
总下发: <%= totalWithdraws %>｜<%= (totalWithdraws/exchangeRate).toFixed(2) %> <%= unit %>
余: <%= balance %>｜<%= (balance/exchangeRate).toFixed(2) %> <%= unit %>